tips.text: Had a yummy lunch! The Tom Yam chicken was delicious and affordable-- the meat was juicy and tender, and the rice was flavoured nicely. The egg of course was the icing on the cake-- just divine! :D
Sarawak noodles with BBQ chicken wings and a glass of ice lemon tea totally hits the spot.
Their coke/sprite float limited time for $1.50 only! Such a big cup with ice cream! Really worth it! & their fish burger at $2 :) try them wat u waiting for?
